Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了营救被蓝染虏走的织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入虚圈的一护等人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突进破面们的老巢虚夜宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡在与加廷拜恩战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内的新能力得以觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在突然出现的十刃之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伊多拉的面前无力招架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...切 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很弱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是发过誓的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好要活着回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会对那些不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入这虚圈的家伙们的愚昧感到生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 与阿洛尼洛对峙的露琪亚也陷入了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力叫做"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬死亡之虚 将其能力和灵压为我所用的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙以志波海燕的身体返回虚圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我整个给吞噬掉才得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体就是志波海燕的灵体本身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内所有的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑中所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都完好地保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是将这些记忆和经历 读取出来再行动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓十刃的刀剑解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在恐惧着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再感到恐惧一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是至今为止 我所吞噬掉的所有虚的力量显现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以为十刃的刀剣解放 和一般的破面差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将所有吞噬掉的虚的能力 全部同时表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止所吞噬的虚的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三万三千六百五十
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将是超过三万的虚之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一个人的对战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我...就只能到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我杀害了海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才使得海燕大人的灵体落入虚的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为救自己而杀害了海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你...我的心...才得以留存
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人的身体从敌人手里夺过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少这一点是对海燕大人的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在心里告诉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎这一点...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有挥剑的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对海燕大人的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已没有挥剑的...力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见...了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊 海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我怎么叫你 摇你 你都不回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一落枕怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落枕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一边走路一边睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你丢下咯 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风吹到脸上的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林分出我前行的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草木的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你到哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一棵棵的树木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安 兴奋和温暖交织在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼之欲出的这份情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是西流魂街三区北端的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲤伏山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次带我修行的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是新入队员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是副队长志波海燕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边可是副队长在跟你报名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该自报家门 并请我多多指教才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫朽木...露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK了 露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的怒声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的下级与上级的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三番队欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们队上的队长身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是我在管理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也可以偶尔叫错 称我为海燕队长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这种平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却正是我所追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够呢 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟儿飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一瞬间我被鸟分散了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二击就被海燕大人从左下方攻入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切我都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是非常专注的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是想吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个超级自我中心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不是的啦 海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海...海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱扔出了鞘的刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都会肚子饿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着这么害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的我 心中有所不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入队仪式顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的能力还无法...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一入队马上就成为席官...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就缺乏剑术的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知罪梦之壁 仅立其上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破道之三十三 苍火坠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在灵术院时鬼道的成绩还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在护廷队中也只属一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以呆在护廷十三队中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟为了什么而呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟为了什么而在这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情不是明摆着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了守护而战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要守护什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么...你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啦 那个啦 很多东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来实在是很模糊不清的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其它更明确一些的回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明确的回答啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木 你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有听过我们队长的一贯主张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗分为两种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护生命的战斗和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫尊严的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是浮竹队长的一贯主张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得无论哪种战斗 最终都是在守护相同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相同的东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃... 好酸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我可是很认真地在说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我问你啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得"心"在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是在这... 附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得 心啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你接触的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就在我们之间生成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心不在身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思索什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想念谁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就在那里生成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界上只有自己孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不存在什么心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人确实是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么好烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你衷心希望能呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你的心就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这就是你呆在这里的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来你战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事绝对不能做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的身体就是魂魄本身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死后身体自然会化作尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为包围尸魂界的灵子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时心会去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心要交给同伴保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给同伴...保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将心交给同伴保管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就会在那个人体内继续生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能独自死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心要交给同伴保管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有意识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命真大 不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎样苟延残喘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法改变你不能斩杀我的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留有握刀柄的力气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你想起了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用折断的刀战斗的蠢事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太碍眼了 放下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心的所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身体里确实是海燕大人的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 海燕大人并不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经交给我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十刃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 蓝染大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我跟着你 就会从一切痛苦中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好痛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要 我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对...不会...认同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别死啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解什么是孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为被捕者的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解什么是喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴前来搭救时的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那些同伴受伤被打倒时的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在... 就去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伊多拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天您用手指 指着地面是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是用这种方法 寻找整个虚夜宫中的灵压
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情也可以做得到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 泰斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们别无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有钱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次的预算已经用得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太乱花钱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长您用得最多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 为了快速凑集经费
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拍些名人的生活照来卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在现世搞偷拍的狗仔师都赚了大钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是护廷十三队的明星们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
